    "summary": "Supermetrics exposes a REST API at `https://api.supermetrics.com`, a streamable-HTTP MCP server at `https://mcp.supermetrics.com/mcp`, and a `supermetrics` CLI; all require authentication, primarily via Supermetrics-issued API keys, with the CLI also supporting user OAuth login.",
