        "type": "oauth2",
        "label": "Supermetrics user OAuth login",
        "setup": "Run `supermetrics login` in the CLI and complete the browser sign-in with your Supermetrics account (Google/Microsoft login). The CLI stores and auto-refreshes the OAuth tokens. For MCP, the server docs say it also supports OAuth, but the public docs/spec do not clearly document self-service client registration or client setup, so the easiest confirmed acquisition path is the CLI login flow.",
